PN,34801
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782362902
OL,3,CRail passengers in the West Midlands
OL,4,Cwarned of reduced services during
OL,5,Cheatwave
OL,7,FRail operators in the West Midlands
OL,8,Fare warning "significantly-reduced"
OL,9,Ftrain services will be running across
OL,10,Fthis week due to the forecast heatwave.
OL,12,FThe UK is expected to experience
OL,13,Fexceptionally-high temperatures over
OL,14,Fthe coming days.
OL,16,FA rare red warning for extreme heat is
OL,17,Fexpected to come into force on the
OL,18,Fmorning of Wednesday, June 24, across
OL,19,Fparts of the region.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782362902
OL,3,CRail passengers in the West Midlands
OL,4,Cwarned of reduced services during
OL,5,Cheatwave
OL,7,FSome areas in the West Midlands are
OL,8,Falso forecast to reach 39C on
OL,9,FWednesday and Thursday.
OL,11,FAs people are being urged to take
OL,12,Fcare, rail passengers are also being
OL,13,Fadvised to check their journeys before
OL,14,Ftravelling on Tuesday and to only
OL,15,Ftravel on Wednesday and Thursday if
OL,16,Ftheir journey is essential.
OL,26,@pD@ZOX
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782362902
OL,3,CRail passengers in the West Midlands
OL,4,Cwarned of reduced services during
OL,5,Cheatwave
OL,7,FJonny Wiseman, West Midlands Railway
OL,8,Fcustomer experience and commercial
OL,9,Fdirector, said: "With extremely high
OL,10,Ftemperatures forecast over the coming
OL,11,Fdays we will be running a
OL,12,Fsignificantly reduced service across
OL,13,Four network for safety reasons.
OL,15,F"We advise our customers to check
OL,16,Fbefore travelling on Tuesday and to
OL,17,Fonly travel on Wednesday and Thursday
OL,18,Fif their journey is essential."
OL,26,@zD@_O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782362902
OL,3,CRail passengers in the West Midlands
OL,4,Cwarned of reduced services during
OL,5,Cheatwave
OL,7,FThe operator says extreme heat can
OL,8,Fcause rails to expand and buckle, so
OL,9,Fwhen temperatures reach certain
OL,10,Fthresholds, trains must run more
OL,11,Fslowly to keep services safe.
OL,13,FAmended timetables will be uploaded to
OL,14,Fjourney planners overnight and routes
OL,15,Fwith a reduced service level from
OL,16,FTuesday include:
OL,18,FNetwork Rail says passengers on the
OL,19,FChiltern network have been advised
OL,20,Fthat train timetables will be reduced
OL,21,Fdue to extremely hot weather.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782362902
OL,3,CRail passengers in the West Midlands
OL,4,Cwarned of reduced services during
OL,5,Cheatwave
OL,7,FDenise Wetton, Network Rail's Central
OL,8,Froute director, said: "With red
OL,9,Fweather warnings in place across the
OL,10,Fcountry for extreme hot weather,
OL,11,Fservices across the West Midlands will
OL,12,Fbe reduced this week.
OL,14,F"While all railway lines will remain
OL,15,Fopen, running fewer trains will help
OL,16,Fus manage the impact of the hot
OL,17,Fweather and keep passengers and
OL,18,Fcolleagues safe.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782362902
OL,3,CRail passengers in the West Midlands
OL,4,Cwarned of reduced services during
OL,5,Cheatwave
OL,7,F"We strongly advise customers to plan
OL,8,Fahead, check their journey before
OL,9,Ftravelling and consider whether their
OL,10,Ftrip is absolutely necessary on the
OL,11,Fhottest days.
OL,13,F"If you do need to travel, please
OL,14,Fallow extra time, carry water to stay
OL,15,Fhydrated and be prepared for services
OL,16,Fto be busier than usual.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782362902
OL,3,CRail passengers in the West Midlands
OL,4,Cwarned of reduced services during
OL,5,Cheatwave
OL,7,F"We are working closely with our train
OL,8,Foperator partners to keep people
OL,9,Fmoving safely, but there is likely to
OL,10,Fbe disruption and journeys may take
OL,11,Flonger than normal.
OL,13,F"Please check for the latest travel
OL,14,Finformation before setting off."
OL,16,FElsewhere, East Midlands Railway says
OL,17,Ftickets dated Tuesday, June 23,
OL,18,FWednesday 24 and Thursday 25, can be
OL,19,Fused at no extra cost to travel on
OL,20,Fearlier services on the same day.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
